General.Name: M Yochananof and Sons Ltd
General.Description: M.Yochananof and Sons (1988) Ltd engages in the marketing and retail trade in the food and related products in Israel. The company offers dairy products, pharma and cleaning products, fresh and frozen meat, fruits and vegetables, fish products, grocery, beverages, frozen goods, and bakery. M.Yochananof and Sons (1988) Ltd was incorporated in 1988 and is based in Rehovot, Israel.
